author: Lord Cinister
title: Lord Cinister
text:
Bought the Windows 10 Pro license after extensive research (sounded too good to be true) but all the reviews were positive. So I used a low limit card and within minutes I got my key-code.
I had a problem trying to upgrade my Home edition to Pro and the online chat solved that in the first response. I am very impressed by this company.
Do it believe me you wont regret it.
